RasterFunctionTemplate.Name: COP30_HAND_2SDstretch
RasterFunctionTemplate.Description: Applies a 2 Standard Deviation stretch using Dynamic Range Adjustment (DRA).

Function.Name: Stretch Symbology
Function.Description:
Enhances an image by adjusting the range of values displayed. This does not alter the underlying pixel values. If a pixel has a value outside of the specified range, it will appear as either the minimum or maximum value.
This symbology uses a Standard Deviation (n=2) stretch making use of Dynamic Range Adjustment (DRA).
